Beth O'Rourke, 44, of Paxton, Massachusetts, has spent the past 7 years fighting stage four biliary cancer and passed away April 16 .
On April 16, the mother of Courtney, 11, and Seamus, 8, lost that fight to cancer .
'I was a survivor. I loved a long run, to sit quietly by the lake, to read and dance and be silly with my sisters and friends, until tears ran down our legs!' she wrote .
As for her own life, she said she hoped to be remembered 'with laughter, love and a good pint'